            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDaniel%2011%3A36-12%3A13%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_36%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20king%20will%20do%20as%20he%20pleases%2C%20exalting%20himself%20and%20claiming%20to%20be%20greater%20than%20every%20god%2C%20even%20blaspheming%20the%20God%20of%20gods.%20He%20will%20succeed%2C%20but%20only%20until%20the%20time%20of%20wrath%20is%20completed.%20For%20what%20has%20been%20determined%20will%20surely%20take%20place.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_37%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20have%20no%20respect%20for%20the%20gods%20of%20his%20ancestors%2C%20or%20for%20the%20god%20loved%20by%20women%2C%20or%20for%20any%20other%20god%2C%20for%20he%20will%20boast%20that%20he%20is%20greater%20than%20them%20all.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_38%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3EInstead%20of%20these%2C%20he%20will%20worship%20the%20god%20of%20fortresses%26%23x2014%3Ba%20god%20his%20ancestors%20never%20knew%26%23x2014%3Band%20lavish%20on%20him%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20precious%20stones%2C%20and%20expensive%20gifts.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_39%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2239%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E39%3C%2Fspan%3EClaiming%20this%20foreign%20god%26%23x2019%3Bs%20help%2C%20he%20will%20attack%20the%20strongest%20fortresses.%20He%20will%20honor%20those%20who%20submit%20to%20him%2C%20appointing%20them%20to%20positions%20of%20authority%20and%20dividing%20the%20land%20among%20them%20as%20their%20reward.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A39%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eat%20a%20price.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_40%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2240%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E40%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20end%2C%20the%20king%20of%20the%20south%20will%20attack%20the%20king%20of%20the%20north.%20The%20king%20of%20the%20north%20will%20storm%20out%20with%20chariots%2C%20charioteers%2C%20and%20a%20vast%20navy.%20He%20will%20invade%20various%20lands%20and%20sweep%20through%20them%20like%20a%20flood.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_41%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2241%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E41%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20enter%20the%20glorious%20land%20of%20Israel%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A41%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20glorious%20land.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20many%20nations%20will%20fall%2C%20but%20Moab%2C%20Edom%2C%20and%20the%20best%20part%20of%20Ammon%20will%20escape.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_42%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2242%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20conquer%20many%20countries%2C%20and%20even%20Egypt%20will%20not%20escape.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_43%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2243%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E43%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20gain%20control%20over%20the%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20treasures%20of%20Egypt%2C%20and%20the%20Libyans%20and%20Ethiopians%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A43%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ECushites.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20be%20his%20servants.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_44%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2244%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E44%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20then%20news%20from%20the%20east%20and%20the%20north%20will%20alarm%20him%2C%20and%20he%20will%20set%20out%20in%20great%20anger%20to%20destroy%20and%20obliterate%20many.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_11_45%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2245%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E45%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20stop%20between%20the%20glorious%20holy%20mountain%20and%20the%20sea%20and%20will%20pitch%20his%20royal%20tents.%20But%20while%20he%20is%20there%2C%20his%20time%20will%20suddenly%20run%20out%2C%20and%20no%20one%20will%20help%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_1%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDaniel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Time%20of%20the%20End%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAt%20that%20time%20Michael%2C%20the%20archangel%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20great%20prince.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20stands%20guard%20over%20your%20nation%2C%20will%20arise.%20Then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20time%20of%20anguish%20greater%20than%20any%20since%20nations%20first%20came%20into%20existence.%20But%20at%20that%20time%20every%20one%20of%20your%20people%20whose%20name%20is%20written%20in%20the%20book%20will%20be%20rescued.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_2%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EMany%20of%20those%20whose%20bodies%20lie%20dead%20and%20buried%20will%20rise%20up%2C%20some%20to%20everlasting%20life%20and%20some%20to%20shame%20and%20everlasting%20disgrace.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_3%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThose%20who%20are%20wise%20will%20shine%20as%20bright%20as%20the%20sky%2C%20and%20those%20who%20lead%20many%20to%20righteousness%20will%20shine%20like%20the%20stars%20forever.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_4%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%2C%20Daniel%2C%20keep%20this%20prophecy%20a%20secret%3B%20seal%20up%20the%20book%20until%20the%20time%20of%20the%20end%2C%20when%20many%20will%20rush%20here%20and%20there%2C%20and%20knowledge%20will%20increase.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_5%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%2C%20Daniel%2C%20looked%20and%20saw%20two%20others%20standing%20on%20opposite%20banks%20of%20the%20river.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_6%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20asked%20the%20man%20dressed%20in%20linen%2C%20who%20was%20now%20standing%20above%20the%20river%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHow%20long%20will%20it%20be%20until%20these%20shocking%20events%20are%20over%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_7%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20man%20dressed%20in%20linen%2C%20who%20was%20standing%20above%20the%20river%2C%20raised%20both%20his%20hands%20toward%20heaven%20and%20took%20a%20solemn%20oath%20by%20the%20One%20who%20lives%20forever%2C%20saying%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20will%20go%20on%20for%20a%20time%2C%20times%2C%20and%20half%20a%20time.%20When%20the%20shattering%20of%20the%20holy%20people%20has%20finally%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20all%20these%20things%20will%20have%20happened.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_8%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20heard%20what%20he%20said%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20what%20he%20meant.%20So%20I%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHow%20will%20all%20this%20finally%20end%2C%20my%20lord%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_9%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20now%2C%20Daniel%2C%20for%20what%20I%20have%20said%20is%20kept%20secret%20and%20sealed%20until%20the%20time%20of%20the%20end.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_10%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EMany%20will%20be%20purified%2C%20cleansed%2C%20and%20refined%20by%20these%20trials.%20But%20the%20wicked%20will%20continue%20in%20their%20wickedness%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20will%20understand.%20Only%20those%20who%20are%20wise%20will%20know%20what%20it%20means.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_11%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BFrom%20the%20time%20the%20daily%20sacrifice%20is%20stopped%20and%20the%20sacrilegious%20object%20that%20causes%20desecration%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20abomination%20of%20desolation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20set%20up%20to%20be%20worshiped%2C%20there%20will%20be%201%2C290%20days.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_12%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20blessed%20are%20those%20who%20wait%20and%20remain%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%201%2C335%20days!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_12_13%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAs%20for%20you%2C%20go%20your%20way%20until%20the%20end.%20You%20will%20rest%2C%20and%20then%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20days%2C%20you%20will%20rise%20again%20to%20receive%20the%20inheritance%20set%20aside%20for%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E"
